snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Sanctus Reach - Legacy of the Weirdboy Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Legacy of the Weirdboy is out!

http://store.steampowered.com/app/623140/Warhammer_40000_Sanctus_Reach__Legacy_of_the_Weirdboy/

In the first DLC for Warhammer 40,000: Sanctus Reach you are Big Redd da Warphead and lead the Greenskins in a quest to vanquish the Space Wolves defending the planet of Alaric Prime!
